Heart of Freedom
	KEY:Heart of Freedom ~ Steel Falcon
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary
	DESC:You gain a +4 morale bonus to saving throws against charm and compulsion effects and attempts to possess your body or mind.
	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

Enemy of Slavers
	KEY:Enemy of Slavers ~ Steel Falcon
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary
	DEFINE:EnemyofSlaversBonus|0
	DESC:You gain a +%1 bonus on Bluff, Knowledge, Perception, Sense Motive, and Survival checks against slavers and slave-owners. Likewise, you get a +%1 bonus on weapon attack and damage rolls against them. This is treated as a favored enemy bonus. If you have a favored enemy bonus from another class and your target is a slaver as well as a favored enemy of another type, the bonuses do not stack, and you simply use whichever bonus is higher.|EnemyofSlaversBonus
	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

Sailor and Survivalist
	KEY:Sailor and Survivalist ~ Steel Falcon
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary
	DESC:You add your level to Profession (sailor) checks and Survival checks to get along in the wild and navigate in the wilderness.
	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

Heroic Speech
	KEY:Heroic Speech ~ Steel Falcon
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural
	DEFINE:HeroicSpeechDuration|0
	DEFINE:HeroicSpeechBonus|0
	DESC:You can inspire your allies with tales of greatness, heroism, and the ideals of Andoran. This functions like the inspire courage aspect of bardic performance, treating the Steel Falcon class level as your bard level for determining the effect; if you are also a bard, both class levels stack when determining the effect of this ability and the effect of your inspire courage bard ability. You can use this ability a number of rounds per day equal to your Steel Falcon level plus your Charisma modifier.
	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

Luck of the Eagle
	KEY:Luck of the Eagle ~ Steel Falcon
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary
	DESC:You can reroll any one d20 roll, but you must take the new roll, even if it is lower.
	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

Superior Aid
	KEY:Superior Aid ~ Steel Falcon
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary
	DESC:When performing the aid another action, you grant a +4 bonus on the ally’s attack or to the ally’s Armor Class instead of the normal +2.
	SOURCEPAGE:p.22

